info.name: Un Owen Was Her Plus
info.description: Based on the popular Touhou character Flandre Scarlet and the color schemes of Castlevania. This theme can be used for the many facets of Google.
info.additionalInfo:
Version 3

1.1 Added logo to Google Main page; bugfixes
1.2 Colorfixes; made Youtube search in G+ more visible
1.3 Colorfixes; Improved Calendar functionality
1.4 colorfixes; Made a more visible share button
1.5 Colorfixes; Support for all Non-English Google, Thanks Malthinae
1.6 Colorfixes; support for new notifications, removed modded google bell for superior new Google Bell; fixed domain issues
1.7 Added support for Google Photos
1.8 Fixed domain change from talkgadget to hangouts.google.com; colorfixes
1.9 New G+ Changes
